description: This file declares the interface for the Beep Page Container Object, including creation, removal, object enrollment, and initialization functions for the environment. It provides prototypes for the exported functions that other components can call.

methods.name: BeepCreatePageContainer
methods.description: Creates a new Page Container object with provided context handles.

methods.name: BeepPcoCreate
methods.description: Creates a new Beep Page Container object with provided context handles.

methods.name: BeepPcoRemove
methods.description: Removes the specified Page Container object.

methods.name: BeepPcoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects into the Page Container object.
